{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_019F7m9np5ypmZgYD2wixvLJ","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→Lamb\n     2→Stew\n     3→\n     4→A traditional recipe that celebrates the finest seasonal ingredients. The combination of flavors creates a harmonious blend that delights the palate.\n     5→Tradycyjny sposób przygotowania, który gwarantuje doskonały smak i doskonałą teksturę.\n     6→A beloved family recipe that has stood the test of time. Prepare with patience and attention to detail for best results.\n     7→This dish represents the very best of home cooking traditions. Serve warm to fully appreciate its complex flavors.\n     8→This classic dish brings warmth and comfort to any table. Perfect for family gatherings, it's been passed down through generations with love and care.\n     9→\n    10→INGREDIENTS:\n    11→\n    12→2 cups flour\n    13→2 teaspoons baking powder\n    14→2 tablespoons olive oil\n    15→Salt and pepper to taste\n    16→¾ cup milk\n    17→2 onions, diced\n    18→2 cups vegetables\n    19→\n    20→INSTRUCTIONS:\n    21→\n    22→1. Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).\n    23→2. Mix dry ingredients in a large bowl.\n    24→3. In another bowl, combine wet ingredients.\n    25→4. Fold dry ingredients into wet mixture.\n    26→5. Pour into prepared pan.\n    27→6. Bake for 25-30 minutes until golden.\n    28→7. Cool before serving."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01SD8AA9LDu7w4NHpurCkETj","session_id":"fc97eaa2-7481-42f4-b7bf-89f7efc643c7","uuid":"506447de-9cf9-4bc1-9a01-3226be5f670b"}
