{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01XmWxCRa8Znvf5QJtwBhP6i","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→SEZON: WIOSNA\n     2→\n     3→Beet Salad\n     4→\n     5→This dish represents the very best of home cooking traditions. Serve warm to fully appreciate its complex flavors.\n     6→Tradycyjny sposób przygotowania, który gwarantuje doskonały smak i doskonałą teksturę.\n     7→Originating from ancient culinary traditions, this preparation method ensures maximum flavor extraction and nutritional retention.\n     8→This classic dish brings warmth and comfort to any table. Perfect for family gatherings, it's been passed down through generations with love and care.\n     9→\n    10→INGREDIENTS:\n    11→\n    12→3 eggs\n    13→2 cups flour\n    14→2 teaspoons baking powder\n    15→3 cloves garlic\n    16→1 pound beef\n    17→½ cup butter\n    18→2 tablespoons olive oil\n    19→\n    20→INSTRUCTIONS:\n    21→\n    22→1. Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).\n    23→2. Mix dry ingredients in a large bowl.\n    24→3. In another bowl, combine wet ingredients.\n    25→4. Fold dry ingredients into wet mixture.\n    26→5. Pour into prepared pan.\n    27→6. Bake for 25-30 minutes until golden.\n    28→7. Cool before serving."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01SD8AA9LDu7w4NHpurCkETj","session_id":"fc97eaa2-7481-42f4-b7bf-89f7efc643c7","uuid":"c79b0ca1-0615-438c-b7a0-4f8e8e04b5bc"}
