{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01WyQM81PKvfTZM2cs7HyTU7","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a comprehensive understanding. Let me outline my approach before writing the plan.\n\n**Key proposed changes:**\n\n1. **Pattern 1 (ALL_CAPS → Title Case, ~20 failures):** Add a `toTitleCase()` normalization as the final output step. When the extracted title is ALL_CAPS, convert to Title Case while preserving short prepositions lowercase. This is the single biggest win.\n\n2. **Pattern 2 (`ze` garbled filter):** Add Polish prepositions `ze`, `bo`, `na`, `ni`, `po`, `ku`, `od` to `commonShort2`. One-line fix.\n\n3. **Pattern 3 (dedup destroys joins):** Invert the dedup direction for multi-line joins: when a join and its component singles all survive, protect the join by removing the singles instead. The join is structurally stronger evidence of a complete title.\n\n4. **Pattern 4 (section label blocks joins):** Allow joins starting with section labels when the combined phrase has ≥3 words (a category word + modifiers = title, not a standalone category header).\n\n5. **Pattern 5 (long garbage prologue, ~12 failures):** Replace the `findBurstEnd` < 20 char limit with a content-based garbage detector: lines matching cooking-instruction patterns (imperative verbs, ingredient phrases) before the first title-like candidate are noise.\n\n6. **Pattern 6 (SEZON:):** Add `SEZON:` to `METADATA_PATTERNS`.\n\n7. **Pattern 7 (parenthetical over-merge):** Strip parenthetical English glosses `(English Subtitle)` from candidates after merge — detect by mixed-case content inside parens when the base is ALL_CAPS.\n\n8. **Pattern 8 (compound title dedup):** Give position-0 candidates immunity from \"shorter wins\" dedup when the shorter candidate appears later in the document.\n\n9. **Pattern 9 (page number prefix):** Extract title after stripping leading `\\d+\\s+` from lines that match page-number format."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":604,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2819,"cache_read_input_tokens":45024,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2819},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"fc97eaa2-7481-42f4-b7bf-89f7efc643c7","uuid":"311700de-d583-4ac1-b473-85a9f3944bad"}
